{"tid":1998772,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)新舊忍者龜","createTime":"2020-05-02T15:57:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T20:34:16.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"01a3873bcab8feb588ddde3e893c78394fbd5a76","tid":1998772,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T15:57:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新沙士已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=eQX%2BqlmYp67lP1AM6ayufSHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=12d8d57c\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=eQX%2BqlmYp67lP1AM6ayufSHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=84e798e5\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=eQX%2BqlmYp67lP1AM6ayufSHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=e9dc8378\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/7/75/Teenage_Mutant_Ninja_Turtles_poster_(1990_film_Version).jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F7%2F75%2FTeenage_Mutant_Ninja_Turtles_poster_%281990_film_Version%29.jpg&h=c97a8c20&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/a/a3/Teenage_mutant_ninja_turtles_ver15.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fa%2Fa3%2FTeenage_mutant_ninja_turtles_ver15.jpg&h=adbf7e6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.話說在紐約市的下水道之中住著四隻功夫高強的忍者龜，它們跟隨著忍者師父&mdash;一隻來自日本的超級大老鼠。一次偶然機會，它們救了一名正義的電視女記者，她也成為了唯一知道忍者龜藏身處的人。在多次行俠仗義後，他們與城市裡的一個神秘組織結怨。這個組織招募了很多無知的青少年，教他們功夫，同時也指示他們做壞事。<br />\n在神秘組織的一次突襲後，由於寡不敵眾，忍者神龜受了重傷，同時，他們的老師也被這個神秘組織抓去..<br />\n<br />\n2.忍者神龜們發現了變種物質的洩漏之處，但史萊德同時也發現這一秘密，於是他們之間又展開了新一輪的戰鬥，而忍者神龜們也在戰鬥中得到了提高........<br />\n<br />\n3.城市需要英雄來拯救，黑暗降臨紐約，大反派施萊德和他率領的異族用鐵腕壓制一切，從警察到政客都被其所控制。神龜們和無畏的女記者愛普莉爾以及聰明的攝像師菲諾通力合作，摧毀施萊德的恐怖計劃，讓這座城市重新恢復寧靜<br />\n<br />\n4.故事承接前集，忍者龜李奧納多、米開朗基羅、多納太羅和拉斐爾在擊退踐踏者後，再次挺身而出對抗捲土重來的許瑞德和從天而降的外星機械敵人，避免紐約受到威脅。此外，忍者龜們、艾波和凡諾還意外地認識了新戰友凱西&middot;瓊斯<br />\n<br />\n12 00AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=eQX%2BqlmYp67lP1AM6ayufSHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=f7099870\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=eQX%2BqlmYp67lP1AM6ayufSHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=4130e2cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"095fc9eb0fb10c0d7f1eaedf96a78133d3f8fee0","tid":1998772,"uid"